title: 2016 Travvy Awards: Vote Now For Your Favorites!
text:
Last updated: 09:25 AM ET, Thu October 08 2015 2016 Travvy Awards: Vote Now For Your Favorites! Travel Agent | Courtney Love | October 08, 2015 
For several months, the industry’s hottest suppliers, destinations and travel professionals have been submitting their entries to win this year’s Travvy Awards. Now in its second year, the 2016 Travvy Awards have quickly positioned themselves as the most prestigious award in the industry today, voted on by those who know travel best – travel professionals and their customers. 
How are Travvy winners selected? Winners of a Travvy will be identified as the best of the best in the industry through a rigorous judging process. With over 175 awards this year, we need your help in determining who will win not only the impressive Travvy statuette, but also a place among the industry’s elite. < Do you want to read the full story? You must be a registered travel professional with an active account to view the full story. Are you a Travel Agent? Log in to your account now, or register for free!
